<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #2c5282; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .section { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .reference { background: #ebf8ff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center; }
        .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 30px; }
        .thank-you { font-size: 1.2em; color: #2c5282; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Cyber Threat Report Confirmation</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p class="thank-you">Thank you for reporting a potential cyber threat!</p>

            <div class="section">
                <p>Dear {{#if report.reporter_info.name}}{{report.reporter_info.name}}{{else}}Concerned Citizen{{/if}},</p>
                
                <p>We have received your report about a suspicious URL. Your report has been forwarded to the MP Cyber Cell for investigation.</p>
                
                <div class="reference">
                    <h3>Your Reference ID</h3>
                    <p style="font-size: 1.2em; font-weight: bold;">{{reference_id}}</p>
                    <p>Please keep this ID for future reference.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h3>Report Summary</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Reported URL:</strong> {{report.url}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Threat Type:</strong> {{report.threat_type}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Submission Time:</strong> {{report.timestamp}}</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
                <ol>
                    <li>The MP Cyber Cell will review your report</li>
                    <li>They may contact you for additional information if needed</li>
                    <li>Appropriate action will be taken based on the investigation</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <p>If you notice any other suspicious cyber activities, please don't hesitate to report them through our platform.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated confirmation from the MP Cyber Safety Platform.</p>
            <p>For urgent matters, please contact the MP Cyber Cell directly.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 